{"tid":947147,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢賊偷電動車電瓶被電死　家屬反索償　車主賠5萬人民幣精神損失費","createTime":"2018-12-19T05:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T10:55:02.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8205a9f1b2e310423e2a62de4f7a0b951a7a5af3","tid":947147,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181219/s00004/ac6a2c8ac8968b2303db004852f85601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181219%2Fs00004%2Fac6a2c8ac8968b2303db004852f85601.jpg&h=15e44b54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地武漢一名男子疑偷竊電動車電瓶時觸電死亡，男子家屬反要求車主賠償20萬元，車主最終就範，賠償家屬5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n劉姓車主早前將電動車停泊路邊，為電瓶通宵充電，一名男子欲偷去其車上電瓶，惟大雨導致電瓶漏電，男子觸電死亡。男子家屬其後反要求車主賠償，堅持索價20萬元人民幣，最終在法庭調解下，車主賠償5萬元的精神損失費。<br />\n<br />\n有網民批評判決「有失公允且毫無道理」，認為法庭允許賠償是縱容小偷行為。亦有網民斥男子「自食其果」，他涉偷竊在先，不值得同情。<br />\n<br />\n(北京青年報/網易新聞)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181219/s00004/1545189093026/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181219%2Fs00004%2F1545189093026%2F&d=jwGvS68r2ymNx0b%2BIwoJjf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=5db8f32b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181219%2Fs00004%2F1545189093026%2F&h=f8e343e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181219/s00004/1545189093026/</a>"},{"pid":"b73eceae800dc84120997531abab8aab98d07b21","tid":947147,"uid":74262,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5331c144b0b4c654c0da05620554804d6e752f40","tid":947147,"uid":64009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b73eceae800dc84120997531abab8aab98d07b21","tid":947147,"uid":74262,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"